<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_218_r2l23">Hercʒog <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von Bayrn </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_218_r2l24"><expan>Gnedıg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / Vns hat <expan>fürg<ex>elegt</ex></expan> <expan>vlr<ex>ich</ex></expan> futrer <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> . vvie </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_218_r2l25">daʒ ſein Sun vlrich in <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> land vnd gepyete </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_218_r2l26">bey prawnaw gefangen ſey worden <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr ewr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_218_r2l27">gnade durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>wıllıg<ex>en</ex></expan> dinſt <expan>wılle<ex>n</ex></expan> darcʒu <expan>vvende<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_218_r2l28">wollet / daʒ der <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>B<ex>urgers</ex></expan> ſun ledig werde Als etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_218_r2l29">das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc </ab>
