</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_218" id="108r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Herczog <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von Bayrn </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, uns hat
                                                  <expan>fürg<ex>elegt</ex></expan>
<expan>Ulr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Futrer,
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, wie daz sein sun
                                                Ulrich in <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> land und
                                                gepyete bey Prawnaw gefangen sey worden.
                                                  <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir ewr gnade
                                                durch <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>willig<ex>en</ex></expan> dinst
                                                  <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> darczu
                                                  <expan>wende<ex>n</ex></expan> wollet, daz der
                                                  <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urgers</ex></expan> sun ledig werde. Als
                                                etc. Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.</ab>
</div>
